===Noun===
'''контроль''' (kontról’) {{m}}, [[контроли]] (kontróli) {{p}}

#[[control]].
#[[checkup]], [[check]]ing, [[inspection]], [[monitoring]], [[supervision]], [[verification]].
#[[blank test]], [[standard]].
#[[institution]] or [[organization]] that carries out such checks, inspections or monitoring.
#area at the entrance to a theater where tickets are checked or collected.
#''(informal)'' [[ticket-collector]]s, [[inspector]]s.

